java.lang.Object
LLQueue<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
KQueue<T>
public class LLQueue<T> extends Object implements KQueue<T>
This class contains a constructor and methods for a Queue object which holds a list where elements are entered into the back and removed from the front.
